</span>
<style>
.framework-icon{display:inline-grid;width:var(--icon-size);height:var(--icon-size);place-items:center;flex:none}.framework-icon svg{display:block;max-width:100%;max-height:100%;overflow:visible}.framework-icon--react{color:#149eca}
</style>
